Test Prep Courses

Study.com's test prep courses will help you earn a top score on the ACT, SAT, AP, GRE, GMAT and other standardized exams. Learn on your own schedule with our engaging, self-paced video lessons. Choose a course below and get started!

How It Works

  • Choose a test prep course: Browse our collection of test prep courses for high school students and prospective graduate students. We can help you get ready for exams including the ACT, SAT, GRE and TOEFL.
  • Watch entertaining video lessons: Illustrated video lessons make concepts covered on your exam easy to commit to memory.
  • Test your knowledge with practice quizzes: Complete each lesson by taking a short quiz to see how well you've absorbed the material. Chapter quizzes and practice final exams are also available.
  • Get help from our expert instructors: Ask our experienced instructors questions about any exam topic.

Who Our Courses Are For

  • Students studying for high school exit exams
  • Students preparing for the ACT, SAT or AP subject tests
  • Students getting ready to take college placement exams
  • Students applying to graduate or professional school

Why Our Courses Work

  • Access to all courses: Your subscription gets you access to all of our test prep courses and study guides. Plus, you can view course content as often as you'd like.
  • Specialized instruction: Test prep courses are tailored to exam content. You'll not only find out what's covered on the test you're taking, but also get information about exam formatting and scoring.
  • Practice quizzes and tests: Courses feature plenty of practice problems similar to the ones you'll encounter on test day, so you can go into your exam fully prepared.
